title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Sim Update 5 - Did performance really improved
description:
A few days back Asobo released Sim Update V. Earlier it was announced that  one of the improvements in this Sim Update would be the performance resulting. In this video we will monitor the FPS during a flight starting a Rotterdam The Hague Airport (EHRD) which prior to Sim Update V showed values of sometimes 15 FPS.

After take off we will set course to Rotterdam City which has a lot of custom addons and look at the impact on the FPS and once we passed the city we continue to fly east to see what the highest FPS value is we can hit.
